CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 21, 1959, pg. B2, reads: "GIRL SCOUT COOKS - These young ladies, shown with their troop leader, are Girl Scouts from Troop 1303, and they are engaged in earning a cooking badge. Left to right: Delores Jones, Phyllis Edwards, Irma Dennis, Ann Smith, Joyce Elliot and Mrs. Sadye Wilborn, troop leader. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Girl Scouts from troop 1303, from left: Delores Jones, Phyllis Edwards, Irma Dennis, Ann Smith in background, Joyce Elliot, troop leader Sadye Wilborn, and unknown on right, earning cooking badge in Equitable Gas demonstration kitchen
